斷這是非法以炸藥捕魚的行為。有專家慨嘆，近年中國漁業資源枯竭，與中國漁民絕子絕孫的「毀滅性捕撈」方式有關<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20170610/20050854\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170610%2F20050854&d=aRUSysLZ%2BeaNkx2Uih%2FT4jOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=2d3f56bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170610%2F20050854&h=2bfadce6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20170610/20050854</a>"},{"pid":"fb04e5c12f12e3280c43c2105de5e1f4ff18f83f","tid":567632,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他國家漁民，捉到小魚唔過某個長度就會放生，強国漁民就大小通吃，一定絕種啦[img]assets/faces/lny/angel.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n未受過教育部既野蠻動物係咁"},{"pid":"d61219322d239ed1d92e085da01c8eacd38d8173","tid":567632,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb04e5c12f12e3280c43c2105de5e1f4ff18f83f","tid":567632,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:32:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其他國家漁民，捉到小魚唔過某個長度就會放生，強国漁民就大小通吃，一定絕種啦[img]assets/faces/lny/angel.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n未受過教育部既野蠻動物係咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:33:39.000Z","msg":"世界癌症<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12fec502c479ed242038a50f01b0db3d156aee9f","tid":567632,"uid":123956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"過度捕魚的惡果,最好全世界餓死所以蝗蟲,到蝗會自相殘殺和分裂,一定比中東血腥"},{"pid":"ca6008968906d4c06466fa462827a47934c82c1c","tid":567632,"uid":164799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T00:37:57.000Z","msg":"吳京又可以拍埋海戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"h